high_descs: Turn left, move forward, then turn left again to approach the bed.
Pick up the cell phone from on the bed.
Turn around, move forward, then turn left to approach the dresser.
Place the cell phone in the bowl, on the dresser.
Pick up the bowl with the cell phone in it.
Turn around, go straight, then turn right to approach the desk.
Put the bowl on the rightmost corner of the desk.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a cell phone in it on the desk.

high_descs: turn left and walk forwards a bit, then turn left and walk to the bed at the end of the room
grab the cellphone off of the bed to the left of the laptop
move to the right side of the room where the dresser is to the right of the bed
place the cellphone inside of the glass bowl which is on top of the cabinet there
pick up the glass bowl with the cellphone in it
turn around and walk to the end of the room, then turn right and walk forwards until you reach the desk
place the bowl down on the right side of the desk
anns.task_desc: place a bowl with a cellphone in it on the right side of the desk

high_descs: Turn around and face the bed where the computer sits open.
Pick up the phone from the bed.
Turn and walk to face the night stand next to the bed.
Put the phone in the glass bowl on the night stand.
Pick up the bowl with the phone in it from the night stand.
Turn around and walk to the desk and stand in front of the computer.
Set the bowl on the right side of the desk, to the right of the computer.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a phone in it on a desk.
